-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_historico_zonas
-- as
SELECT
   [CHAVE_ZONA]
,[DATA_ZONA]
,[STATUS_ZONA]
,[NUM_DATA_ZONA]
,[MES_ZONA] 
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_historico_zonas.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH ([CHAVE_ZONA]			VARCHAR(100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
            ,[DATA_ZONA]            VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
            ,[STATUS_ZONA]          VARCHAR(100) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
            ,[NUM_DATA_ZONA]        VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
            ,[MES_ZONA]             VARCHAR(25) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8) AS ROW
